Step 1: install node (see https://www.airpair.com/javascript/node-js-tutorial)

'''curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/creationix/nvm/v0.13.1/install.sh | bash
nvm install v0.10.31
node -v (check that install worked)
nvm alias default 0.10.31'''

Step 2: navigate to directory where you want to download folders
eg. cd ~/Documents

Step 3: download this code and navigate to folder
git clone https://github.com/katiecanada/Gayle_sms
cd Gayle_sms

Step 4: install node modules in the Gayle_sms folder
[sudo] npm install twilio
npm install express
npm install express3-handlebars
npm install mongodb
npm install mongoose
npm install serve-favicon
